        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "- There wants nothing, said I, to make it so but the comic use which the gallantry of a Frenchman would put it to,--to make love the first moment, and an offer of his person the second.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
