        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_191322_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/191322/3595_191322_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "That selfish people hate it for their own; -",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_191322_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/191322/3595_191322_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "Hypocrites for heaven's; -",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_191322_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/191322/3595_191322_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "Then I solemnly declare, said the lady, blushing, you have been making love to me all this while.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_191322_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/191322/3595_191322_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "CALAIS.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_191322_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/191322/3595_191322_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "Monsieur Dessein came back to let us out of the chaise, and acquaint the lady, the count de L, her brother, was just arrived at the hotel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "Blue vision of depth lost in height,--sea and sky interblending through luminous haze.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "The day is of spring, and the hour morning.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "Only sky and sea,--one azure enormity...",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "In the fore, ripples are catching a silvery light, and threads of foam are swirling.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000002_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000002_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "But a little further off no motion is visible, nor anything save color: dim warm blue of water widening away to melt into blue of air.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "Horizon there is none: only distance soaring into space,--infinite concavity hollowing before you, and hugely arching above you,--the color deepening with the height.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "But far in the midway blue there hangs a faint, faint vision of palace towers, with high roofs horned and curved like moons,--some shadowing of splendor strange and old, illumined by a sunshine soft as memory.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "...What I have thus been trying to describe is a kakemono,--that is to say, a Japanese painting on silk, suspended to the wall of my alcove;--and the name of it is Shinkiro, which signifies \"Mirage.\" But the shapes of the mirage are unmistakable.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "Thus much is told of the place in the Chinese books of that time:--",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "In Horai there is neither death nor pain; and there is no winter.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "The flowers in that place never fade, and the fruits never fail; and if a man taste of those fruits even but once, he can never again feel thirst or hunger.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "All this and more is told in the legends of the time of the Shin dynasty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "For really there are no enchanted fruits which leave the eater forever satisfied,--nor any magical grass which revives the dead,--nor any fountain of fairy water,--nor any bowls which never lack rice,--nor any cups which never lack wine.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "Nevertheless there are wonderful things in Horai; and the most wonderful of all has not been mentioned by any Chinese writer.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "I mean the atmosphere of Horai.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "It is an atmosphere peculiar to the place; and, because of it, the sunshine in Horai is whiter than any other sunshine,--a milky light that never dazzles,--astonishingly clear, but very soft.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "This atmosphere is not of our human period: it is enormously old,--so old that I feel afraid when I try to think how old it is;--and it is not a mixture of nitrogen and oxygen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000007_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000007_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "Whatever mortal man inhales that atmosphere, he takes into his blood the thrilling of these spirits; and they change the sense within him,--reshaping his notions of Space and Time,--so that he can see only as they used to see, and feel only as they used to feel, and think only as they used to think.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000007_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000007_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "Soft as sleep are these changes of sense; and Horai, discerned across them, might thus be described:--",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "--Because in Horai there is no knowledge of great evil, the hearts of the people never grow old.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "And, by reason of being always young in heart, the people of Horai smile from birth until death-except when the Gods send sorrow among them; and faces then are veiled until the sorrow goes away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "All folk in Horai love and trust each other, as if all were members of a single household;--and the speech of the women is like birdsong, because the hearts of them are light as the souls of birds;--and the swaying of the sleeves of the maidens at play seems a flutter of wide, soft wings.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "In Horai nothing is hidden but grief, because there is no reason for shame;--and nothing is locked away, because there could not be any theft;--and by night as well as by day all doors remain unbarred, because there is no reason for fear.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "--Much of this seeming would be due to the inhalation of that ghostly atmosphere-but not all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "For the spell wrought by the dead is only the charm of an Ideal, the glamour of an ancient hope;--and something of that hope has found fulfillment in many hearts,--in the simple beauty of unselfish lives,--in the sweetness of Woman...",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "--Evil winds from the West are blowing over Horai; and the magical atmosphere, alas! is shrinking away before them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3595_418_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3595/418/3595_418_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3595",
        "content": "It lingers now in patches only, and bands,--like those long bright bands of cloud that train across the landscapes of Japanese painters.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]